text: DeKaylin Zecharius "DK" Metcalf (born December 14, 1997) is an American football wide receiver for the Seattle Seahawks of the National Football League (NFL). He played college football at Ole Miss. He is the son of former NFL guard Terrence Metcalf. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:American football wide receivers Category:Ole Miss Rebels football players Category:Seattle Seahawks players
